{"tid":1977242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"坡狗，你國家又添上新個案了！","createTime":"2020-04-17T20:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T13:42:42.000Z","uid":93141,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e8dfa5714fcbca2b885b73e46ae6c404582ad7a3","tid":1977242,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:39:27.000Z","msg":"新加坡人一起床，所有港台的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，「坡狗，你國家又添上新個案了！」他不回答，自顧自地說，「有足夠貨物供應」便排出九包CSI口罩。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又把異見者綁起來打籐了！」坡狗睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白?我前天親眼見有人說了李家的壞話，吊著打。」坡狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「維穩不能算極權&hellip;&hellip;維穩！&hellip;&hellip;人民幣的事，能算極權麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「Monkey see monkey do」，什麼「如果真的吃那麼多飯和即食麵，肯定腸胃炎」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑得咳起來：國內外充滿了武漢肺炎。"},{"pid":"0899292d86c506d52cc9ad91cb4a4ffaee86cd84","tid":1977242,"uid":282347,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:40:19.000Z","msg":"monkey see monkey sick<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad2de133085b2004480df473160e32c8fc5cf53","tid":1977242,"uid":212119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:41:34.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"ec67e682de9dc006da1e46d7edcc7a4f4f7b0cc1","tid":1977242,"uid":93141,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fad2de133085b2004480df473160e32c8fc5cf53","tid":1977242,"uid":212119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:41:34.000Z","msg":"ok"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:42:41.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔出科普出廢文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfb78d46f9a78adba95773775e932d18332d49b","tid":1977242,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T20:43:51.000Z","msg":"改名叫坡猴啦"},{"pid":"f020d00d559e01aff062ef5390d6c4dc5fc55123","tid":1977242,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":